Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次失敗不像平常的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.61,0:01:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後不許再有失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.38,0:01:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則即使你是神風隊隊長 也不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.58,0:01:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我謹記在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.22,0:01:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道你身份的佐佐木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.55,0:01:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有別外那兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要早點殺他們滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.69,0:02:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐佐木平八郎已是拿劍的廢物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外兩人 其中一人 只是泛泛之輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.90,0:02:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很容易就可以解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.30,0:02:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那剩下的那一個呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.50,0:02:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是傳說的流浪劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.37,0:02:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪劍客？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.09,0:02:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？是棘手人物嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒還不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.16,0:02:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我親手就可解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.73,0:02:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的計劃已經快成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時都要做好萬全準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.20,0:02:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的達成後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.74,0:02:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬 我打算派你當要職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.64,0:02:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能受您的器重是我的榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.75,0:02:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十六話\N勇氣的誓言\N燃燒吧！秘劍紫電太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起！左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意！反正我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.96,0:03:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再說 能為私塾盡力也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 對方為了滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可能會襲擊 你和緋村先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.90,0:03:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿！要殺我可沒那麼容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心的話 就更不用擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師你應該知道劍心的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.11,0:03:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你面前雖然不方便說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是緋村先生和東馬交手時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬的確略勝一籌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別說笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心可是天下無敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你看錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！這點緋村先生應該也清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.77,0:03:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道那傢伙真比劍心強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.25,0:04:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來左之助的朋友\N是京都巡捕組的劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.22,0:04:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那私塾老師\N過去竟然曾和劍心交過手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人生的際遇真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火野派一刀流秘劍[紫電太刀]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 你好帥喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好帥！好帥！禰彥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫電太刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.26,0:04:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是能使出這種劍法\N竟然已經棄劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想真有點可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.47,0:04:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是讓孩子實現夢想\N認真教書不也很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小綾也要好好唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當個偉大的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小雀也要唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺聽了真高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個要加油喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喲！小姐 劍心在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.82,0:05:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？劍心 不是在洗衣服嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗衣服？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？人怎麼不見了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.83,0:05:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼一副擔心的樣子 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心有什麼好擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼了？左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.85,0:05:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是叫東馬吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.42,0:05:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有沒有什麼遺言？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就此認命吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.49,0:05:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅髮與臉頰的十字刀疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是傳說中的 斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？為什麼不拔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.30,0:06:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來的目的只是有事要問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們為何自稱為神風隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還從事暗殺活動？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如斬人拔刀齊過去所為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.51,0:06:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想用這把劍立足於世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我過去的確殺過人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.32,0:06:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是用暗殺絕對擋不住維新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.99,0:06:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我這把劍 不殺人的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！要除掉這些敗類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有比用劍更有效的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說到了明治時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.33,0:06:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為劍而生的我\N在什麼時代都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.17,0:06:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用這劍立足於世\N主宰自己的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.54,0:06:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰指使你用劍殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.01,0:06:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多問也沒有用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔劍吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要取斬人拔刀齊的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.86,0:06:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有點可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過你是逃不過我這把劍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火野派一刀流秘劍[紫電太刀]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.83,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我你個忠告吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.84,0:07:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的劍法和佐佐木平八郎不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我自己練出的 最強的劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩！今晚嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可撿回了一條命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我隨時都可取你性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可回去先洗洗頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓人擔心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.65,0:08:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來已經鎖定下個目標了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說又要暗殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論有什麼理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人就是不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定是我的緣故…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.97,0:08:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的東馬像極了過去的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？東馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.07,0:08:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師您擔任京都巡捕組組長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.04,0:08:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同為火野派一刀流弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也與有榮焉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.82,0:08:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恭賀老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.42,0:08:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也聽說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不久也可向京都邁進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們過不久就可出師了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.93,0:08:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.23,0:08:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在維新志士在京都橫行\N造成全國動盪不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.73,0:08:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了救我們的國家\N只有殺他個片甲不留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.14,0:08:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師！我也想早日殺敵報國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定會到京都去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.61,0:08:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您一定要等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.11,0:09:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到京都斬人不容易呀！東馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.78,0:09:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已決心為劍而生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論維新志士是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都要親手殺了他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.39,0:09:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太偏激了 東馬…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.26,0:09:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時我真的以為用一把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.33,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能阻止維新志士 保護國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再一次！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.07,0:09:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時東馬這麼崇拜我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.47,0:09:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後練功時也都強調一刀見血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.08,0:09:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是今後日本\N需要的不再是動刀舞劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.38,0:09:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬可說是\N生錯時代 可憐的犧牲品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我也有責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.46,0:09:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了不讓他再加重罪孽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.66,0:09:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我非阻止東馬不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可輕舉妄動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.00,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師你已是棄劍之人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.23,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！這絕不是老師的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.61,0:10:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一個就輪到山縣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個頑石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.75,0:10:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前我和大商人結伙\N就和他結下樑子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政治與金錢掛鉤\N本來就理所當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不是嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行動就在今晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.96,0:10:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會到迎賓館參加晚宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.70,0:10:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家路上襲擊他易如反掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.83,0:10:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是神風隊要怎麼處理？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.97,0:10:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要照他們的希望安排嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.71,0:10:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成任務後 就將全隊解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.88,0:10:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這時期 暗殺還能行得通嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.22,0:10:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是蒙在鼓裏的一群笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？劍心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我們有一群不速之客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這夥人是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.52,0:11:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.76,0:11:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山縣陸軍上將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橋爪先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近不太平靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回去時要小心吶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的提醒我會牢記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永別了 山縣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.99,0:11:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們好好看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.96,0:12:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和成為流浪劍客的拔刀齊\N棄劍的佐佐木平八郎不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要以劍客身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續在明治時代生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為此 我要用這把劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.97,0:12:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證明我能立足於這世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.08,0:12:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山縣來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們上！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手實在太差了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就像飛蛾撲火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.74,0:12:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不只你們這些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.04,0:12:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人在哪 要襲擊誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不會講！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦！是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.51,0:12:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想說也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能老師太手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過打人我可在行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.65,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到山縣陸軍上將的馬車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.33,0:13:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們神風隊替天行道來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會是你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.87,0:13:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我有話要對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.38,0:14:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬 雖然你有一番理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.58,0:14:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜卻淪為奸詐政治家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用來爭權奪利的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想侮辱我們神風隊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們被蒙在鼓裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總有一天會真相大白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.07,0:14:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,廢話少說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.77,0:14:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來怎樣都不會相信我的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰都無法阻止我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.58,0:14:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止神風隊的人 格殺勿論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.28,0:14:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不明白嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來白費口舌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.79,0:14:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住嘴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.59,0:14:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.49,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還說什麼要去提水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐佐木老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.27,0:15:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個也不留給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.27,0:15:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真不夠意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是老樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐佐木老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.98,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再錯下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.42,0:15:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快覺醒吧！東馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.62,0:15:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些過氣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.33,0:15:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好一口氣殺你們滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部給我殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來對付你 拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.73,0:15:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用這把劍\N讓你斬人拔刀齊連名帶人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這世上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那招式是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.63,0:16:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的紫電太刀是勝過\N佐佐木平八郎的 最強劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.01,0:16:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就試試看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.78,0:16:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙太刀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.59,0:17:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.43,0:17:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼他的雙太刀\N能躲過我的紫電連牙太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.53,0:17:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂紫電連牙太刀 東馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.81,0:17:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他躲得過你第一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.08,0:17:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能立即使出雙太刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.05,0:17:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你的劍流自然會變弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後雙太刀就已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.05,0:17:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 緋村先生 已經看出你的破綻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果第一擊沒刺中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.49,0:17:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紫電太刀就失去效果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.83,0:17:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你所謂的替天行道\N不過是殺人的劍法罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.01,0:17:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒在那裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是神風隊暗殺集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.96,0:18:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部逮捕起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.36,0:18:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村先生 這次又麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.13,0:18:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪兒的話 我還好 倒是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橋爪先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.60,0:18:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神風隊暗殺的\N全都是與你對立的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.34,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神風隊的幕後指使人\N就是橋爪參議員你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.55,0:18:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼都不知道\N我沒見過這些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一概不知 你們有何證據？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.59,0:18:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再狡辯了 橋爪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經逃不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺悟吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是陷阱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是無辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊 你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.44,0:18:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的確被利用 成為殺人工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,橋爪 納命來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救救我！我認罪就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.48,0:19:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已認罪 快阻止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.02,0:19:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是嗜血殺人魔\N只要活著一定會殺我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託！快殺了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還不想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐佐木老師！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我死 老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少還有武士的尊嚴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.11,0:19:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在死的話就是懦夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.51,0:19:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東馬 你罪孽深重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.18,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不論犯了什麼罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.65,0:19:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有認罪服刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.19,0:19:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能向之前所殺的人贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐佐木老師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.50,0:19:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是身為師兄的我\N能教你的最後一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.37,0:20:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師 你不是說不再拿劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.58,0:20:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！對…對不起！左之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.95,0:20:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這玩意可以丟到水溝裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.63,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都看著我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.43,0:20:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎？山縣將軍嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此事當真？左之助？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！那陸軍上將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.87,0:20:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到老師原來是京都\N巡捕組組長佐佐木平八郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.44,0:20:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚇得壽命頓時減少十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧！劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.85,0:20:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定過去曾和老師交手過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心裏還餘悸猶存吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.55,0:20:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過現在已是私塾老師了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我不是說了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.12,0:20:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的斬人二劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.43,0:20:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心以逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師以學問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.20,0:21:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後不再殺人反而是助人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那左之助最好也學老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拋開過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.90,0:21:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你的壞習慣和髒話改一改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪有什麼壞習慣 這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.31,0:21:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還敢說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.01,0:21:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個不要吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.78,0:21:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你也阻止他們一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之說的不無道理啊！

